info.name: Customization Project Web API
info.description: The collection contains examples from the [Manipulating Customization Projects by Using the Web API](https://help.acumatica.com/(W(42))/Help?ScreenId=ShowWiki&pageid=7eddb850-0096-41c3-8ea7-14becf6401ff) chapter of the Customization Guide of Acumatica ERP.

request.description: This example shows how to sign in to Acumatica ERP. This process is described in [Sign In to the Service](https://desktop.postman.com/?desktopVersion=10.6.0&userId=1878971&teamId=0).

request.description: This example shows how to initiate publication of one or multiple customization projects in an Acumatica ERP instance. This process is described in [Customization Project Web API: publishBegin](https://help.acumatica.com/(W(45))/Help?ScreenId=ShowWiki&pageid=ead25ada-37bd-45a6-9523-4c1bb597edf6).

response.name: Start Publication of a Customization Project

request.description: This example shows how to check whether publishing of customization projects has been completed in an Acumatica ERP instance. This process is described in [Customization Project Web API: publishEnd](https://help.acumatica.com/(W(45))/Help?ScreenId=ShowWiki&pageid=3c488227-e436-4f16-b7f4-707912ce2e1d).

response.name: Check for Publication Completion

request.description: This example shows how to retrieve the list of published customization projects from an Acumatica ERP instance. This process is described in [Customization Project Web API: getPublished](https://help.acumatica.com/(W(45))/Help?ScreenId=ShowWiki&pageid=b56850c5-6c74-4c5a-99b3-7f87f3a90b72).

request.description: This example shows how to retrieve the content of a customization project from the database of an Acumatica ERP instance. This process is described in [Customization Project Web API: getProject](https://help.acumatica.com/(W(45))/Help?ScreenId=ShowWiki&pageid=e3acf7da-9b70-433e-81d5-f7095deb7538).

This example shows how to unpublish all customization projects that are currently published in an Acumatica ERP instance. This process is described in [Customization Project Web API: unpublishAll](https://help.acumatica.com/(W(45))/Help?ScreenId=ShowWiki&pageid=d4e4e796-43cc-45bf-9bc1-54f43af2cb5e).

This example shows how to remove a customization project from in an Acumatica ERP instance. This process is described in [Customization Project Web API: delete](https://help.acumatica.com/(W(45))/Help?ScreenId=ShowWiki&pageid=9209661b-07a0-4529-b7bd-9c67ae3499a6).

This example shows how to sign out from Acumatica ERP. This process is described in [Sign Out from the Service](https://help.acumatica.com/(W(45))/Help?ScreenId=ShowWiki&pageid=f6701ec1-2296-4155-8242-03d29006bf6e).
